onboarding_subtitle1: Generate images that reflect your unique vision & style.
onboarding_subtitle2: Discover a world of artistic possibilities.
onboarding_subtitle3: Refine your creations, providing intelligent insights to elevate your art.
enter_prompt_message: Describe anything, Let our app create magic for you.
negative_prompt_message: Tell the model what not to generate.
your_prompt_message: Describe your prompt in a few words
premium_version_message: Enjoy our premium version with more creativity!
select_your_preferred_language_msg: You will use the same language through out the app
panorama_image_description: A panorama image is a wide-angle image that captures a field of view of approximately 180 degrees or more.
upscale_image_description: If you want to upscale the given image resolution two times (2x). If the requested resolution is 512 x 512 px, the generated image will be 1024 x 1024 px.
guidance_scale_description: Higher guidance scale will result in an image that is more similar to the prompt, while a lower guidance scale will result in an image that is more creative and less predictable
image_quality_description: Higher image quality will result in a more detailed image, but will also take longer to generate.
prompt_language_message: Select the language of your prompt. This will help the model to generate better results.
prompt_history_message: Select a prompt from your previously generated prompts.
face_fix_description: Face Fix will fix the face in the generated image.
steps_message: Select the number of denoising steps to generate the image. A higher number can lead to more detailed images but takes longer to process.
name: Name
close_app_msg: Are you sure you want to close the app?
please_try_again_with_appropriate_prompt: Please try again with appropriate prompt content
saftey_check_description: A checker for NSFW images. Any content that is violent, sexual, or offensive will be replaced with black image.
delete_prompt_message: Are you sure you want to delete this prompt?
